page.title: 07ALAKA'S DAY
page.content: I woke up at 6.26 a.m.,I couldn't get back to sleep so I got up at 7.03. Dressed myself and went down to mum.I washed and cleaned myself then left home and went to pick up my friend on the way to school.First we had registration then Biology and Maths. At dinner we had egg on toast with chips (and sauce!).We went back to school and had English and Art.I was really tired so I was glad to get home.For tea we had home-made pizza,it was scrumptious.First of all I watched a bit of "telly" and at 7.00p.m. went to my grandma's house.There I watched more T.V. and played cards.When we got home we had dinner.After this I was so tired that I went to sleep straight away.
